    tmp = wp.sin(wp.cos(wp.abs(tmp + 0.30)))
    v1 = ((wp.cos(v2 + 0.10) / (v0 + 0.85 * v2 + 0.61)) * wp.sin((tmp + 0.37 * v2 + 0.24)))
    v2 = wp.abs(0.19)
    v0 = 0.11
